  ATMOSPHERE: (0..40) "; Hygiene tests for user-defined macros."
  ATMOSPHERE: (40..41) "\n"
  ATMOSPHERE: (41..42) ";"
  ATMOSPHERE: (42..43) "\n"
  ATMOSPHERE: (43..113) "; The classic `my-or` uses a `temp` binding in its expansion template."
